  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为新的快照生成系统画一个完整的架构图。核心需求是：用户通过Web和移动端上传内容，后端要处理异步的快照生成任务。我想先确认一下整体的分层结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User Layer",
        "Client Applications",
        "Core Backend Services"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。那客户端这边，Web端用Next.js，移动端是React Native还是Flutter？我需要确定技术栈来标注。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "frontend-web",
        "frontend-mobile"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Web端确定用Next.js加Tailwind。移动端目前还在评估，可以写成React Native / Flutter。另外，安全层面我们需要Cloudflare做第一道防线，然后有一个PHP的网关层专门处理验证码验证。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cloudflare",
        "gateway-php"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把网关和安全层画出来了：Cloudflare负责DDoS和WAF，然后是一个PHP中间件做验证码校验。接下来核心API用什么技术栈？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Cloudflare",
        "gateway-php"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "核心API用Python的FastAPI，承载主要业务逻辑。然后数据层比较特殊——我们主体用Firebase全家桶，但网关相关的快照队列任务要单独放到MySQL里。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "backend-api",
        "Firebase Platform",
        "MySQL Database"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Firebase全家桶具体包含哪些组件？Auth、Firestore、Storage这些都有吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Firebase Authentication",
        "Firestore",
        "Cloud Storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，需要四个：Firebase Authentication做用户身份，Firestore存用户资料、元数据和帖子内容，Cloud Storage存媒体和快照文件，再加上Cloud Functions跑异步任务，特别是快照生成。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Firebase Authentication",
        "Firestore",
        "Cloud Storage",
        "Cloud Functions"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我把Firebase平台作为一个子图展开，里面包含这四个组件。现在来理一下连接关系：用户先到Web或Mobile App，然后走HTTPS到Cloudflare？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "frontend-web",
        "frontend-mobile",
        "Cloudflare"
