    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，Web和Mobile都要经过Cloudflare。然后Cloudflare把流量打到PHP网关，网关验证完之后才转发到FastAPI后端。",
